# This file lists core dependencies for building and running the project.

C++17 or newer
SFML 2.6.1    # Simple and Fast Multimedia Library

# Linux (Debian/Ubuntu): 
#   Download SFML 2.6.1 from https://www.sfml-dev.org/download/sfml/2.6.1/
#   or use package manager if version 2.6.1 is available

# macOS (Homebrew):
#   brew install sfml

# Windows:
#   Download and install SFML 2.6.1 from https://www.sfml-dev.org/download/sfml/2.6.1/
